<span id="freeTextContainer11882910581189043022">There are two books that I&apos;ve read that have blown my mind and this is one of them. It&apos;s written so well. It&apos;s a view point I had never known about or considered. It&apos;s about the relationship between Heinrich Himmler and his personal physician Felix Kersten. It&apos;s an amazing story and everyone should know it. Dr. Kersten is an amazing human who took the most horrible job in history and turned it into a rescue mission. I would highly recommend it. </span>
