  <div class="friendReviews elementListBrown" >
    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_2352031986" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2352031986" />
    <a title="Florence Primrose" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1424248-florence-primrose"><img alt="Florence Primrose" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1387405312p2/1424248.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2352031986?book_show_action=true">Apr 05, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Florence Primrose" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Florence Primrose" href="/user/show/1424248-florence-primrose">Florence Primrose</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2352031986" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11405849462704963083">Kirsten, a massage therapist, in the late 1930s, began taking care of Himmler, Hitler’s right-hand man, and relieved his stomach pain for five years. In the midst of treating him he got promises from Himmler to save both small and large groups of prisoners and even Jews.<br/><br/>It was fascinating to learn what Kirsten could achieve with his treatment even though he was suspected by many of the Nazis due to his influence on Himmler and often feared for his life.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


