<span id="freeTextContainer16620615946774916563">Amazing and little known story of massage-therapist Dr. Felix Kersten and his relationship to<br/>Reichsfuhrer Heinrich Himmler. Kersten was able to save millions of lives during WWII with his<br/>considerable influence over Himmler, and was secretly considered one of the most powerful men in<br/>Germany. A fascinating story!<br/></span>

          </span>
