<li class='cover' id='bookCover_94498'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/94498.La_Mort_est_mon_m_tier"><img alt="La Mort est mon métier" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1413128510l/94498._SY160_.jpg" />
